<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ILAB - Virtual STEM Laboratory</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e3a8a);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 40px 20px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #cbd5f5;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px,1fr));
      gap: 15px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .feature {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background: #38bdf8;
      color: #000;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #0ea5e9;
      color: white;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

  <h1>🔬 ILAB</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Interactive Virtual Laboratory for STEM Students</p>

  <div class="card">
    <p>
      ILAB is a modern virtual laboratory designed for STEM learners.  
      It provides interactive activities and simulations that help students understand scientific concepts in a simple and engaging way.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🚀 What You Can Do</h2>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">🧪 Virtual Experiments</div>
      <div class="feature">📚 STEM Learning Basics</div>
      <div class="feature">⚡ Interactive Activities</div>
      <div class="feature">🎯 Easy to Understand Concepts</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🌍 Why ILAB?</h2>
    <p>
      Virtual labs allow students to explore science anytime, anywhere through simulations of real experiments, improving understanding and engagement. 
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- BUTTON -->
  <a href="https://ilab-rt3-12-rhodolite.lovable.app/" class="btn">
    🔗 Open ILAB Now
  </a>

  <footer>
    Developed by <br>
    <strong>ISAIAH RAYNE M. AGPALO</strong><br>
    STEM 12 | Batch 2024–2025
  </footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
